2019-06-27T19:24:15.1103532+03:00 0HLNR3FCQO192:00000001 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("19"ms) [Parameters=["@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [p.Images].[Id], [p.Images].[ForPreview], [p.Images].[Name], [p.Images].[ProductID], [p.Images].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Images] AS [p.Images]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p0].[Id]
    FROM [Products] AS [p0]
    ORDER BY [p0].[Id] DESC
) AS [t] ON [p.Images].[ProductID] = [t].[Id]
